/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔養啦，屋企啲貓見到佢好似見到罐罐咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512dfa1dbb8c4126465f98c5fa06b17399bac8ef","tid":325634,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BB嚟，個咀仲係黃色</blockquote><br />\nBb雀應該養得熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491b1efdb9ff0340b48fea7b65a31ef2dd056fb5","tid":325634,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歡迎加入雀奴嘅世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔養啦，屋企啲貓見到佢好似見到罐罐咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多排熟咗就唔會有敵意㗎啦"},{"pid":"5826b8624e5256ab2c69ba73c35918b2e38c334c","tid":325634,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個都話禽流感，我知危險，但係到頭先咁嘅情況，除非冷血，如果唔係都會幫吓佢啦，一無雨我就會搵地方放佢走，如果唔好彩我中招，未開個post比你地笑吓囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你直頭係香港救星啦如果集雀有病<br />\n困住係你屋企 唔洗走黎走去散播病菌<br />\n前提係你都唔好走報走去<br />\n功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知禽流感係點嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f675dd68352582b77be93ee1d81c98d30f7e27a","tid":325634,"uid":92482,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"吊你地班仆街 周街都有雀啦 唔見你有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   隻雀跌咗落地唔通由得佢比水浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055e772e8d96246db391dc23fa89fd18f4444b50","tid":325634,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢由吹乾左之後就不斷叫，一路無停過，又唔知佢咩事，蟲又食左，水又飲左，屎都屙埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪驚咋？我早幾日都執到隻，但唔肯食野之後過一日就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嗰隻肯食野，但係要將條麥皮蟲一開四先食到，因為我本身養左隻守宮，得啲大條嘅蟲</blockquote><br />\n可能係因為飛行系察覺到蟲系所以好興奮咁叫"},{"pid":"8aa46221e7a964bc545de1a4637af4a4834e6abc","tid":325634,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"八鄉有雀汁咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef6a9f08782f09ea2f554f8b5be20c741737519","tid":325634,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八鄉有雀汁咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想執隻花了哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dd35228b525cad7bd25bce2c7ae6df122aa4ad","tid":325634,"uid":35696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"平日出街不難發現鳥兒滿天飛&nbsp;<br />\n鳥倦知還 飛到累硬係歸巢歇息&nbsp;<br />\n樹上既鳥巢就是牠們唯一的家&nbsp;<br />\n當天氣太惡劣&nbsp;<br />\n係打風落大雨既時候&nbsp;<br />\n樹蔭當然不能百分百阻擋暴雨既吞噬&nbsp;<br />\n平日從鳥巢傳來的吱吱聲彷彿被狂風奪去&nbsp;<br />\n其實鳥兒是否仍然安然無恙？&nbsp;<br />\n還是老早已躲至另一處？"},{"pid":"41282846b6251aa39b1deda0b7ebae927639123b","tid":325634,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平日出街不難發現鳥兒滿天飛&amp;nbsp;<br />\n鳥倦知還 飛到累硬係歸巢歇息&amp;nbsp;<br />\n樹上既鳥巢就是牠們唯一的家&amp;nbsp;<